            <h2>
                Life threatening emergencies in our schools are an ever increasing reality.</h2>
            <h4>
                HOW CAN <b>inSchoolALERT</b> HELP WHEN SECONDS COUNT?</h4>
            <p>
                The <b>inSchoolALERT </b>system provides a mobile app to quickly connect with First
                Responders and immediately notify Teachers, Staff and Administrators of an emergency
                situation, so they can initiate safety procedures while waiting for First Responders
                to arrive.</p>
            <h4>
                HOW IT WORKS</h4>
            <p>
                With the push of a pre-defined button on their smart phone INDIVIDUALS SELECTED
                TO VIEW THE CALL DIRECTORY will</p>
            <p>
                Be connected by phone to the appropriate First Responders</p>
            <p>
                AND the system will</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Initiate an automated push notification, text and email describing the type
                    of incident to only pre-selected contacts such as:</strong></p>
            <ul class="listscl">
                <li>First Responders</li>
                <li>School Administrators</li>
                <li>Teachers and Staff</li>
                <li>Onsite Resource Officers</li>
            </ul>
            <h4>
                Additional Feature of the <b>inSchoolALERT</b> System</h4>
            <p>
                School Administrators can keep the School Community and Public updated with important
                messages by push notification to the app and text messaging anytime the need arises
                by using the ALERT SYSTEM'S NOTIFICATION MODULE.
            </p>
        </div>
